          "date": "2013-01-18 08:44:29.000000000",
          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2643 osc: remove assert for OES_ACTIVE",
        "message": "LU-2643 osc: remove assert for OES_ACTIVE\n\nClient got lock cancel but some part for cancel is actively used\nby client and has OES_ACTIVE state. All cancel locks is high priority\nand hp = 1 for osc_cache_writeback_range(). This cause assert\nLASSERT(hp == 0 && discard == 0)\nThis patch removes the assert, osc_cache will work slower than\ndesigned, probably, but it need to wait clients active work to\nsend pages.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander_boyko@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I9a7e17fbc9de615988c53c36340fd5be9e9dd697\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
